    <entry>
      <title>Riverpod 使用笔记</title>
      <link href="/2026/06/08/Flutter-Riverpod-Notes/"/>
      <url>/2026/06/08/Flutter-Riverpod-Notes/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Flutter中实现状态管理有很多方式，自带的有局限性，且全局管理较为复杂。而三方状态管理库，目前我使用过的有Provider、GetX和Riverpod。Provider比较基础和入门，GetX简单但是过于魔法，路由栈的管理有点乱（因为不需要<code>context</code>就能到处跳）。Riverpod则是Provider的升级版，网上的佬友们都说好，问AI哪个状态管理库好用，基本上都会推荐Riverpod，所以我也就入坑了，就是这样。</p><h3 id="1-安装依赖"><a href="#1-安装依赖" class="headerlink" title="1.安装依赖"></a>1.安装依赖</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">flutter_riverpod:</span> <span class="string">^3.0.3</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-创建状态管理器"><a href="#2-创建状态管理器" class="headerlink" title="2.创建状态管理器"></a>2.创建状态管理器</h3><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">final</span> lightMode = ThemeData(brightness: Brightness.light);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">final</span> darkMode = ThemeData(brightness: Brightness.dark);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/// <span class="language-markdown">主题状态管理器</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">ThemeNotifier</span> <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="title">Notifier</span>&lt;<span class="title">ThemeData</span>&gt; </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="meta">@override</span></span><br><span class="line">  ThemeData build() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 默认使用暗色主题</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> darkMode;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">/// <span class="language-markdown">切换主题</span></span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">void</span> toggleTheme() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    state = state.brightness == Brightness.light ? darkMode : lightMode;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">/// <span class="language-markdown">设置特定主题</span></span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">void</span> setTheme(ThemeData themeData) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    state = themeData;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-创建Provider"><a href="#3-创建Provider" class="headerlink" title="3.创建Provider"></a>3.创建Provider</h3><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/// <span class="language-markdown">主题的 Provider</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">final</span> themeProvider = NotifierProvider&lt;ThemeNotifier, ThemeData&gt;(() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> ThemeNotifier();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-包裹main函数"><a href="#4-包裹main函数" class="headerlink" title="4.包裹main函数"></a>4.包裹<code>main</code>函数</h3><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">void</span> main() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  runApp(</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> ProviderScope(</span><br><span class="line">      child: MyApp(),</span><br><span class="line">    ),</span><br><span class="line">  );</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-使用Provider"><a href="#5-使用Provider" class="headerlink" title="5.使用Provider"></a>5.使用Provider</h3><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">MyApp</span> <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="title">ConsumerWidget</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">const</span> MyApp(&#123;<span class="keyword">super</span>.key&#125;);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="meta">@override</span></span><br><span class="line">  Widget build(BuildContext context, WidgetRef ref) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">final</span> themeData = ref.watch(themeProvider);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> MaterialApp(</span><br><span class="line">      theme: themeData,</span><br><span class="line">      home: Scaffold(</span><br><span class="line">        appBar: AppBar(title: <span class="keyword">const</span> Text(<span class="string">&#x27;Riverpod Theme Demo&#x27;</span>)),</span><br><span class="line">        body: Center(</span><br><span class="line">          child: ElevatedButton(</span><br><span class="line">            onPressed: () &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="comment">// 修改主题状态</span></span><br><span class="line">              ref.read(themeProvider.notifier).toggleTheme();</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            child: <span class="keyword">const</span> Text(<span class="string">&#x27;切换主题&#x27;</span>),</span><br><span class="line">          ),</span><br><span class="line">        ),</span><br><span class="line">      ),</span><br><span class="line">    );</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="补充"><a href="#补充" class="headerlink" title="补充"></a>补充</h3><p>Riverpod还可以直接生成代码，使用代码生成工具跑一下可以自动生成Provider，减少样板代码。这个我用的比较少🤗，后面再研究研究。</p>]]></content>
      
      
